* 4-layer architecture
* Comparison with OSI model
* Real-world usage

### 🔹 3. IP Addressing

* IPv4 and IPv6
* Public vs Private IP
* Static vs Dynamic IP

### 🔹 4. Subnetting

* Subnet masks
* CIDR notation
* Subnet calculations and examples

### 🔹 5. Routing & Switching

* Routers vs Switches
* Routing protocols: RIP, OSPF, BGP
* MAC Address and ARP

### 🔹 6. Network Protocols

* HTTP / HTTPS
* DNS
* FTP
* DHCP

